  "prompt": "How long does it take to claim a Facebook Place?",
  "response": "Claiming a Facebook Place can vary in time depending on several factors. Generally, the process can be quick, often taking just a few minutes to fill out the necessary information and submit your claim. However, the verification process might take longer, usually ranging from a few hours to several days, depending on Facebook's review procedures and the information provided.\n\nTo speed up the process, ensure that you provide accurate information and any documentation Facebook might require to verify your ownership or affiliation with the place. If you encounter any issues, you may need to follow up with Facebook's support.",
